strings: <voice_0x01001C64><se_high>media princess: I always wanted to discuss her. Her name is Prince Handsome.
<voice_0x01001C65><se_high>media princess: We were married long before my grandmother passed away. This is our family contract.
<voice_0x01001C66><se_high>media princess: But I haven't met him yet. No one knows who this guy is.
<voice_0x01001C68><se_high>media princess: specula. If you think there is no water in the pond, think otherwise!
